                                        <Property name="messageText" type="java.lang.String" value="&lt;html&gt;Loads the ground platform from an image. Only takes the colors at index 3, 4, &amp; 8.&lt;br&gt;Supported image formats: PNG or GIF.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Color format should be 4BPP / 16 indexed colors. Images of 8BPP / 256 indexed colors will be converted to 4 BPP / 16 (some colors may be lost).&lt;br&gt;When imported, icons will use the base palette colors.&lt;br&gt;Color index 0 is treated as transparent.&lt;/html&gt;"/>
                                        <Property name="text" type="java.lang.String" value=""/>
